 <purpose>
   The Independent property application module supports a  requirement to
   specify a property independently from a product.  
 </purpose>

 <inscope>
   <li>
     specification of a property independent of its being a property of some product. 
   </li>
   <li>
     specification of relationships and hierarchies of independent properties; 
   </li>
 </inscope>

 <outscope>
   <li>
     assignment of properties to products; 
   </li>
   <li>
     assignment of values to properties. 
   </li>
 </outscope>


